        <li>Use <strong>Tables</strong> to manage Customers and Products.</li>
        <li>Use <strong>Blobs</strong> to upload and display images.</li>
        <li>Use <strong>Queues</strong> to add and view event messages (e.g., order processing).</li>
        <li>Use <strong>Files</strong> to upload and download contracts.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
